wz", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see 1, in six places.       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAzhu", "text_ar": "اجازهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made him to go,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pass along;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAzahu", "text_ar": "جَازَهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he made him to pass through,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "over,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "along and beyond:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, IF, Msb, K;) as also ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bihi", "text_ar": "بِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jAwz", "text_ar": "جاوز", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as will be shown by an ex. below, and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jw~zhu", "text_ar": "جوّزهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and ] ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAzahu", "text_ar": "جَازَهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", for which we find"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jAwzhu", "text_ar": "جاوزهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "incorrectly substituted in the K. (TA.) A rájiz says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "xal~uwA AlT~ariyqa Eano A^abiY say~aAraho\n                      \n                     \n                        Hat~aY yujiyza saAlimFA HimaAraho"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Leave ye the road to Aboo-Seiyárah until he make his ass to pass through,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "over, safely"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S.) And it is said in the Kur [vii. 134, and x. 90],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bibaniY A_isoraAy^iyla AlbaHora", "text_ar": "بِبَنِى اـِسْرَايِيلَ البَحْرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wajaAwazonaA", "text_ar": "وَجَاوَزْنَا", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And we made the Children of Israel to pass through the sea"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) You say also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahumo A_ibilahumo", "text_ar": "لَهُمْ اـِبِلَهُمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaw~aza", "text_ar": "جَوَّزَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tajowiyzN", "text_ar": "تَجْوِيزٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He led for them their camels one by one until they passed."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) ―         -b2-  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made it to pass,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "be current;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jw~zhu", "text_ar": "جوّزهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": as in the following phrases.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajazotu EalaY A@somihi", "text_ar": "اَجَزْتُ عَلَى ا@سْمِهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaEalotuhu jaAy^izFA", "text_ar": "جَعَلْتُهُ جَايِزًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I made his name to pass,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "be current,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by stamping money with it]: (ISk, S, TA:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Darabotu", "text_ar": "ضَرَبْتُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I coined,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "minted,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "money"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in his name"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (ISd, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlD~ar~aAbu Ald~araAhima", "text_ar": "الضَّرَّابُ الدَّرَاهِمَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jw~z", "text_ar": "جوّز", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tajowiyzN", "text_ar": "تَجْوِيزٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The coiner,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "minter,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "made the dirhems,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pieces of money, to pass,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "be current."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "held it, to be allowable,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to pass for lawful; he allowed it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "permitted it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, TA;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jw~zhu", "text_ar": "جوّزهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, TA:) syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~aga", "text_ar": "سَوَّغَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, K:) and syn. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ijaAzapN", "text_ar": "اـِجَازَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [the inf. n. of the former verb,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_i*onN", "text_ar": "اـِذْنٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K, TA: omitted in the CK.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAz lahu maA SanaEa", "text_ar": "اجاز لَهُ مَا صَنَعَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K, *) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lh", "text_ar": "له"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jw~z", "text_ar": "جوّز", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "held, what he did to be allowable,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c. (S, K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEaqolu", "text_ar": "العَقْلُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*aA mim~aA laA yujuw~izuhu", "text_ar": "هٰذَا مِمَّا لَا يُجُوِّزُهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This is of the things which reason will not allow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A, TA.) ―         -b4-  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He granted him the authority or degree of a licentiate in some one or more of the various departments of learning, for the instruction of others therein;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he  granted him a license with respect to the matters that he had related and heard"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from other learned men, to teach the same"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAz lifulaAnK jamiyEa masomuwEaAtihi mino ma$aAy^ixihi", "text_ar": "اجاز لِفُلَانٍ جَمِيعَ مَسْمُوعَاتِهِ مِنْ مَشَايِخِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He ters which he had heard from his sheykhs, to teach the same to others"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) The licentiate is termed ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mujaAzN", "text_ar": "مُجَازٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and the matters which he relates are termed ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mujaAzaAtN", "text_ar": "مُجَازَاتٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAz AlbayoEa", "text_ar": "اجاز البَيْعَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A, Mgh, K,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~ikaAHa", "text_ar": "النِّكَاحَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A, Mgh,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEaqoda", "text_ar": "العَقْدَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Msb,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(the judge, A, Mgh)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "made the sale,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, Mgh, K,) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the marriage,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, Mgh,) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the contract,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to have effect; he executed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "performed it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, Msb K;)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahu", "text_ar": "لَهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for him:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he decreed it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh.) And [in like manner]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAz raA^oyahu", "text_ar": "اجاز رَاْيَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jw~zhu", "text_ar": "جوّزهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made his judgment,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "opinion, to have effect; he executed"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "performed it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) Hence the saying, in a trad. of Aboo-Dharr,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qabola A^ano", "text_ar": "قَبْلَ اَنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yujayzuwA EalaY~a", "text_ar": "يُجَيزُوا عَلَىَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Before they slay me, and execute your order upon me."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)       -A3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajaAzaniY", "text_ar": "اَجَازَنِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K *) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He gave me water for,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he watered"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for me"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], (K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "my land,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "my beasts."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ibilahu", "text_ar": "اـِبِلَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jw~z", "text_ar": "جوّز", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tajowiyzN", "text_ar": "تَجْوِيزٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He watered his camels."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAz Alwafoda", "text_ar": "اجاز الوَفْدَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He gave to the party who came as envoys, or the like, the quantity of water sufficient to pass therewith from one watering-place to another."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajaAzahu maA='F yajuwzu bihi AlT~ariyqa", "text_ar": "اَجَازَهُ مَا=ءً يَجُوزُ بِهِ الطَّرِيقَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He gave him water wherewith to travel the road."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajizoniY", "text_ar": "اَجِزْنِى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA='F", "text_ar": "مَا=ءً"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Give thou me some water that I may go my way, and pass from thee."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Bekr, TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (Aboo-Bekr, TA,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAzhu bijaAy^izapK", "text_ar": "اجازهُ بِجَايِزَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Aboo-Bekr, TA,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AjAzhu bijaAy^izapK saniy~apK", "text_ar": "اجازهُ بِجَايِزَةٍ سَنِيَّةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, A,) (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(the Sultán)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gave him a gift,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "present,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Bekr, TA,) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he gave him a gift,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "present, of high estimation."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A. *) Or the origin of the expression was this: Katan the son of 'Owf, of the tribe of Benoo-Hilál-Ibn-'Ámir-Ibn-Saasa'ah, gave the government of Fáris to 'Abd-Allah Ibn- 'Abbás; and El-Ahnaf passing by him with his army on an expedition to Khurásán, he waited for them upon a bridge, and said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajiyzuwhumo", "text_ar": "اَجِيزُوهُمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Make ye them to pass over"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; and he began to mention the lineage of each man and to give him according to his rank: (S:) or from the fact that a certain commander, having a river between him and an opposing force, said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mano jaAza h`*aA Aln~ahora falahu ka*aA", "text_ar": "مَنْ جَازَ هٰذَا النَّهْرَ فَلَهُ كَذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Whoso passeth this river shall have such a thing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; and whenever one passed over, he received a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAy^izap", "text_ar": "جَايِزَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajaAzahu", "text_ar": "اَجَازَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He gave him."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And it is said in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajiyzuwA Alwafoda binaHowi maA kunotu A^ujiyzuhumo bihi", "text_ar": "اَجِيزُوا الوَفْدَ بِنَحْوِ مَا كُنْتُ اُجِيزُهُمْ بِهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Give ye to the party who come as envoys, or the like, a similar"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAy^izap", "text_ar": "جَايِزَة"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to that which I used to give them."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)"}], "source_